'''Mar Sebastian Valloppilly''' (4 August 1911 – 4 April 2006) was the first bishop of the [[Syro-Malabar Catholic Archdiocese of Tellicherry|Diocese of Tellicherry]] (1953–1989),<ref>Fr. George Thalian: [http://cs.nyu.edu/kandathi/kandathil.html#ext_2 The Great Archbishop Mar Augustine Kandathil, D. D.: the Outline of a Vocation] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120301220721/http://cs.nyu.edu/kandathi/kandathil.html |date=1 March 2012 }}, Mar Louis Memorial Press, 1961.</ref> in [[Kerala]], [[India]]. He was a Gandhian philosopher.

